<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard Notification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #F59E0B;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #F59E0B;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .dashboard-section {
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;
        }
        .qr-section {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff8f6;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 2px dashed #FF6B35;
        }
        .qr-code {
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .qr-code img {
            max-width: 300px;
            height: auto;
            border: 3px solid #FF6B35;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .action-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #F59E0B;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .action-button:hover {
            background-color: #d97706;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ğŸª ZinR Dashboard</h1>
            <p>Your restaurant management dashboard is ready!</p>
        </div>

        <% if (qrCodeDataUrl) { %>
        <!-- QR Code Section -->
        <div class="qr-section">
            <h2>ğŸ“± Your Restaurant QR Code</h2>
            <p>Customers can scan this QR code to access your digital menu and place orders directly from their phones.</p>
            
            <div class="qr-code">
                <img src="<%= qrCodeDataUrl %>" alt="Restaurant QR Code" />
            </div>
            
            <div style="margin: 20px 0;">
                <a href="<%= qrCodeDataUrl %>" download="<%= restaurantName %>-QR-Code.png" class="action-button">
                    ğŸ’¾ Download QR Code
                </a>
                <a href="<%= qrCodeDataUrl %>" target="_blank" class="action-button">
                    ğŸ–¨ï¸ Open for Printing
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>ğŸ’¡ Pro Tip:</strong> Right-click on the QR code image above and select "Save image as..." to download it directly!</p>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="dashboard-section">
            <h3>ğŸš€ Dashboard Features Available</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Restaurant Management:</strong> Update your restaurant details and settings</li>
                <li><strong>Menu Management:</strong> Create categories and add menu items</li>
                <li><strong>Order Processing:</strong> Handle customer orders in real-time</li>
                <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Track your business performance</li>
                <li><strong>QR Code Generation:</strong> Create digital menus for customers</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="dashboard-section">
            <h3>ğŸ“± Access Your Dashboard</h3>
            <p>Log in to your dashboard to start managing your restaurant:</p>
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
                <a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL || 'http://localhost:5173' %>/dashboard" class="action-button">
                    ğŸš€ Go to Dashboard
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Your restaurant is now part of the digital future! ğŸ‰</p>
            <p>Need help? Contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
